  Using from CLI (requires list-calendar-dates and calx)
     % list-calendar-dates -l -m CFA
     % calx -c CFA

DESCRIPTION
    This module provides CFA exam calendar using the Calendar::Dates
    interface.

DATES STATISTICS
     +---------------+-------+
     | key           | value |
     +---------------+-------+
     | Earliest year | 2018  |
     | Latest year   | 2020  |
     +---------------+-------+

DATES SAMPLES
    Entries for year 2019:

